1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:59,920
Whoa! What's up with Song?

4
00:01:00,402 --> 00:01:02,112
(The Other Man)

5
00:01:05,664 --> 00:01:06,880
(Liao)

6
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:11,359
Hello?

7
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:17,760
You are like a concubine
after being summoned.

8
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,719
Lucky you, never been in love.

9
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,400
Don't try it.

10
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,359
It's too sweet.
I'm afraid you couldn't handle it.

11
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,040
Just like you are now.

12
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,719
A game in one hand,
a drink in the other.

13
00:01:29,079 --> 00:01:30,640
And at night, you're on your own.

14
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,680
Song,

15
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:35,319
how are you
both flirtatious and sly now?

16
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,696
Just like

17
00:01:38,144 --> 00:01:39,480
an old dog.

18
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:19,960
Morning.

19
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,599
Weaseling out again?

20
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,919
Make sure you see me clearly this time.

21
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,639
Don't mix me up.

22
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,240
Childish.

23
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:42,800
Me? Childish?

24
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:46,000
Last night you said I know a lot.

25
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,560
You can go.

26
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,159
Burning the bridge?

27
00:02:59,199 --> 00:02:59,808
Ji Xuan,

28
00:03:00,512 --> 00:03:02,280
I really like your cold demeanor.

29
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,392
Do people

30
00:03:03,552 --> 00:03:05,639
in their first relationship
tend to be a bit humble?

31
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,759
Stop it.

32
00:03:09,319 --> 00:03:11,439
I have to go see my mom
at the hospital later.

33
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,159
I'll drive you.

34
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:15,319
Song Zhaoli, we agreed

35
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,479
to keep it from our families.

36
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:18,879
Don't worry.
I'll just wait in the parking lot.

37
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:30,159
You just said Song Zhaoli
didn't come home last night?

38
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,400
Yes, Master.

39
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:35,159
I've looked into everything
you asked about.

40
00:03:36,039 --> 00:03:38,039
Ji Xuan's mother has uremia.

41
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:41,039
Recently, Mr. Song
used all his connections

42
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,639
to find a kidney donor for her.

43
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,360
Also,

44
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:46,840
Ji Xuan and Mr. Song
had contact six years ago.

45
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:48,120
Mr. Song

46
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:50,639
was Ji Xuan's sponsor during college.

47
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,719
Sponsor?

48
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,319
If you had figured it out sooner,

49
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:09,439
you wouldn't have suffered so much.

50
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:16,279
I can manage the company for my brother.

51
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:18,439
But I have one condition.

52
00:04:19,232 --> 00:04:19,839
Go on.

53
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,439
I want to sponsor someone.

54
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,160
Sponsor?

55
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,600
Did you see Wu Rui last night?

56
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,079
No.

57
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:50,000
We've both been busy lately.
Haven't had the chance to meet.

58
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:53,279
You didn't see Wu Rui?
Then what is this?

59
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,439
You and Wu Rui broke up?

60
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,600
Mom, I'll be honest with you.

61
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:07,619
Actually, Wu Rui and I

62
00:05:07,968 --> 00:05:09,519
never actually got together.

63
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:12,920
I only said that to reassure you.

64
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:16,360
I knew it.

65
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,879
You knew?

66
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,319
What kind of young couple

67
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:23,639
goes half a month without calling?

68
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,680
Also,

69
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,000
who meets the girl's parents
for the first time

70
00:05:27,079 --> 00:05:28,169
but happily goes back

71
00:05:28,512 --> 00:05:30,360
to work overtime once being summoned?

72
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,680
Yeah, he didn't play the part.

73
00:05:35,079 --> 00:05:37,680
So, who's your boyfriend now?

74
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,360
Who is it?

75
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,160
Ma'am.

76
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,199
Mr. Song?

77
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,160
Isn't this Wu Rui's boss?

78
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:51,000
The one who came to our place last time.

79
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,079
You remember.
I brought you some supplements.

80
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,000
You're too kind.

81
00:05:58,319 --> 00:06:00,480
Mom, he's my boss now too.

82
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:02,600
Mr. Song,

83
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:05,000
what brings you here today?

84
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,240
I thought you had things to do?

85
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,360
You were hungry last night
and skipped breakfast this morning.

86
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,399
That'll ruin your stomach.

87
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,399
What are you doing?

88
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:15,959
Coming clean.

89
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:19,319
So you two were together last night?

90
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,560
How long have you been together?

91
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,519
Ma'am,

92
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:26,360
ever since Ji Xuan broke up
with Xiao Jin,

93
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,519
I've been pursuing her.

94
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,759
But she never wanted
to make it official.

95
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,759
She even got one of my employees
to pretend to be her boyfriend.

96
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,639
We only made it official last night.

97
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:36,920
But she didn't want me to come see you.

98
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,920
Mom, no...

99
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,759
Don't interrupt.

100
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:41,480
Song, go on.

101
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:44,639
Ma'am, I really like Ji Xuan.

102
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,800
When I was at your place,

103
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,560
seeing Ji Xuan with a new boyfriend,

104
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:49,879
I was so restless.

105
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,720
I might not be able to promise much.

106
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:54,439
But I can promise
I'll protect her with my life.

107
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:57,600
As long as you two feel
you're right for each other,

108
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,040
I have no objections.

109
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,199
Now that we've gotten this far,

110
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:03,000
I'll just come right out.

111
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,192
I feel

112
00:07:04,288 --> 00:07:06,240
it seems Ji Xuan
doesn't like me that much.

113
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:09,079
She's using me as a distraction
during her loneliness.

114
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,000
Song Zhaoli, that's enough.

115
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,040
Is what Song said true?

116
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:18,079
Mom, it's really not what you think.

117
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,399
Song, rest assured.

118
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,600
I will handle this matter for you.

119
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:23,920
Thank you, ma'am.

120
00:07:26,399 --> 00:07:29,000
Song Zhaoli,
if you had a tail right now,

121
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,160
it'd definitely be wagging.

122
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,600
Just okay.

123
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,319
What are you saying?

124
00:07:36,399 --> 00:07:39,040
Ma'am, actually, I wanted to share
some good news with you today.

125
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:40,720
Your body has recovered very well.

126
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:43,079
Transplant surgery is set
for the day after tomorrow.

127
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,879
I've taken care of everything.

128
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,920
Song, thank you for all your trouble.

129
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,480
Great! That's great!

130
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,736
Mr. Liao,

131
00:08:05,312 --> 00:08:06,959
what's this?

132
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:09,839
Your reward: the employee's big meal.

133
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:11,439
Eat more. Don't diet.

134
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:13,680
Strive to knock out ten bad guys
with one punch.

135
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,040
Well,

136
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:19,160
if you're free tomorrow...

137
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,959
Can I take a day off tomorrow?

138
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,079
You have plans?

139
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,800
It's a friend's birthday.

140
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,079
Male or female?

141
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:30,639
Male.

142
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,559
Your crush?

143
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,600
You sleep eight hours a day,

144
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:41,200
spend eight hours with me,

145
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,600
and work another eight hours.

146
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,080
Where did you meet another man?

147
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,720
I met him during my part-time job.

148
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,519
He's a mortician.

149
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,399
And quite handsome.

150
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,320
Do good looks pay the bills?

151
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,440
Are you love-struck?

152
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:58,080
Liao Bei, that's harsh.

153
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,559
I work diligently.

154
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,960
Why can't I date?

155
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,799
Besides, you're my creditor,
not my boyfriend.

156
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:04,799
You can't interfere.

157
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:06,360
You think my words are harsh?

158
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,840
Fine, I'll praise you.

159
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,519
You managed to fall for someone
in such a sacred place.

160
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:11,960
Your love knows no bounds.

161
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,879
Listen, I'm not approving this leave.

162
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,200
Be here on time tomorrow for work.

163
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,120
Or I'll call the police.

164
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,480
You ate more of this meal, so you pay.

165
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,960
It's clear
that Song loves you very much.

166
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:52,320
So, what are your thoughts?

167
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:54,320
He's the CEO of Song Group.

168
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,320
His background
differs entirely from mine.

169
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,360
He likes me now,

170
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:01,720
but I worry
that feelings change over time.

171
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:04,639
Not everyone is like Xiao Jin.

172
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:07,840
Mom, you can't just look
on the bright side of everything.

173
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:10,480
I just want to live in the moment.

174
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,200
What you say makes sense too.

175
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,919
Then decide for yourself.

176
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,600
Wu Shu went MIA on me today.

177
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,600
Ji Xuan, tell her

178
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,759
if I don't know where she is
within ten minutes,

179
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,720
I'll call the police.

180
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:35,080
You like her?

181
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,399
She owes me so much money.
I'm afraid she'll skip town.

182
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,639
Wu Shu is my girlfriend's bestie.

183
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,320
At worst, I'll pay her debt.

184
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,600
Is it about the money?

185
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:49,720
Considering he was once your sponsor,

186
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,679
call Wu Shu and ask her out.

187
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:53,408
Okay.

188
00:10:56,288 --> 00:10:59,104
(Wu Shu)

189
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,240
Hello?

190
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,519
Xuan,

191
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,700
I'm at your company.

192
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:06,159
Where are you?

193
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,559
What's wrong? Why are you crying?

194
00:11:23,412 --> 00:11:25,204
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

195
00:11:25,364 --> 00:11:27,244
♪Flickering neon lights♪

196
00:11:27,444 --> 00:11:30,772
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

197
00:11:31,284 --> 00:11:33,556
♪Every star is♪

198
00:11:33,844 --> 00:11:37,716
♪My heartbeat for you♪

199
00:11:39,028 --> 00:11:40,852
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

200
00:11:41,012 --> 00:11:42,564
♪And land in your arms♪

201
00:11:42,964 --> 00:11:46,420
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

202
00:11:46,676 --> 00:11:49,236
♪In the blue sky♪

203
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:53,428
♪Your smile still lingers♪

204
00:11:54,356 --> 00:11:58,004
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

205
00:11:58,260 --> 00:12:01,924
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

206
00:12:02,132 --> 00:12:05,044
♪Can't find a cure♪

207
00:12:05,044 --> 00:12:09,556
♪To love you after we've parted♪

208
00:12:09,748 --> 00:12:13,780
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

209
00:12:13,780 --> 00:12:17,644
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

210
00:12:17,644 --> 00:12:19,444
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

211
00:12:19,540 --> 00:12:24,692
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

212
00:12:25,332 --> 00:12:29,044
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

213
00:12:29,236 --> 00:12:31,988
♪Can't find a cure♪

214
00:12:32,116 --> 00:12:36,756
♪To love you after we've parted♪

215
00:12:36,924 --> 00:12:40,692
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

216
00:12:40,916 --> 00:12:44,500
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

217
00:12:44,724 --> 00:12:46,764
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

218
00:12:46,764 --> 00:12:51,764
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
